{"tid":1225823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇新聞講英文］CCTVB屌鳩政府視若無睹、忽視民意","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T10:30:40.000Z","uid":49561,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8b6f6561f59b0df9a531fce9bdd5d7dfa2e98d","tid":1225823,"uid":49561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"Elephant in the room (避重就輕)<br />\n<br />\n意思就係 有啲好緊要、好重要嗰啲嘢你就唔講，講埋晒啲小事，大事你又唔夠膽講，當係睇唔到，呢個就係一個Elephant in the room<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就好似《逃犯條例》嗰度下，好多人係好驚架，但係政府就唔想講人哋點解驚，唔想應，that's the elephant in the room!</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newswatchenglish/5cfdb9efe603839e7acf84cf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fnewswatchenglish%2F5cfdb9efe603839e7acf84cf&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=40b58c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newswatchenglish/5cfdb9efe603839e7acf84cf</a>"},{"pid":"e5008de46e713ab1ff35ee63442be7c67bca9400","tid":1225823,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397d5354a68cbf335a55af62ae467d30edb5c84b","tid":1225823,"uid":49561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但推"},{"pid":"f4a92888e5921a86f1a927e27864ddc07a7a452e","tid":1225823,"uid":49561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"TVB清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想瘋狂學英文"},{"pid":"9e8436fa1671ae36d90f374134559845fc814cb3","tid":1225823,"uid":49561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}